  "text": "This paper solves the inverse problem of deriving the LWR model from a non-viscous mean field game among drivers, and also provides basic analysis and numerical solutions of the stationary viscous and non-viscous cases. The paper then extends the model by adding a distributed parameter to the model in terms of travel time which was developed in ( [CITATION_1] - [CITATION_2] ).",
